import axios from"axios";// Export an object containing methods we'll use for accessing the Dog.Ceo API
export default{getUsers:function getUsers(){return axios.get("https://randomuser.me/api/?seed=allusers&results=100");},getUserByName:function getUserByName(name){axios.get("https://randomuser.me/api/?seed=allusers&results=100").then(function(res){return res.filter(function(user){return user.name===name;});});},getBaseNameList:function getBaseNameList(){return axios.get("https://randomuser.me/api/?seed=allusers&results=100?inc=name");}};
